'''lintie''' in [[Quenya]] means "speed" or *"swiftness"
==Etymology==
Stem *''lint'' (probably adjective ''[[linta]]'') with noun ending ''[[-ie]]''.
==Other forms==
*''lintieryanen'' "with his speed" (norne a lintieryanen)<ref>[[Parma Eldalamberon 17]] p.58</ref>
==See also==
*''[[linta]]'' "swift"
